===Noun===
'''Metric structure'''

#In [[music]], '''metric structure''' includes [[metre]], [[tempo]], and all rhythmic aspects which produce temporal regularity or structure, against which the foreground details or [[durational pattern]]s are projected. (DeLone et. al. (Eds.), 1975, chap. 3)

